<span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span> Dr Mandisa Maholwana is the newly appointed CEO of Nelson Mandela Children’s Hospital in Johannesburg. Her experience in healthcare spans close to 20 years. She has a particular interest in working with partners to set up fully integrated healthcare services accompanied by a robust medical information system. Dr Maholwana has vast experience in medical marketing practices, clinical research practices, medical education activities, negotiating with regulatory authorities, and networking with external partners and international funders. Brought to you by Nedbank Private Wealth.